Soul Flex Digitals 'Vintage LP' is a subliminal album featuring 22 tracks of rolling liquid Drum and Bass. This album contains a real versatile range of liquid cuts. Every style of of the Liquid genre is covered. 22 gems from the next generation of Drum and Bass producers. The Vintage LP is the follow up to last years 'Sunday Drive LP' which was recieved really well with many of its tracks reaching the top 10 spots in various download stores. So whether you like vocals, amens, rolling, minimal, dancefloor or atmospheric liquid Drum and Bass you'll find something on this album for you
